  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, your link to the Celestial allows you to serve as a conduit for radiant energy. You have resistance to radiant damage, and when you cast a spell that deals radiant or fire damage, you can add your Charisma modifier to one radiant or fire damage roll of that spell against one of its targets.</p><p>Additionally, when a creature succeeds its saving throw to avoid your Sacred Flame cantrip, you can cause their next saving throw made against your Sacred Flame cantrip to be done at disadvantage until the end of your next turn.</p><p>Furthermore, whenever you roll dice to restore hit points to a creature with your Healing Light, you can roll the dice an additional time, and take the larger amount of healing.</p>",
